{"tid":1340852,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得元朗單嘢其實有啲問題","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T16:19:43.000Z","uid":207374,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"120356ebe1844e950d89b780dc16240628c44be9","tid":1340852,"uid":207374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:16:17.000Z","msg":"政府和新界班牛屎人一直存在不滿<br />\n<br />\n克警又一直掃黃 反白(黑)社會活動<br />\n<br />\n喺政府方面：希望利用鄉黑力量打擊香港人，令香港人收聲。等我地香港人收曬皮再搞班牛屎人，最後就算佢地反政府都無曬班曾經反政府嘅香港人，正喺得番班牛屎人好快俾反黑警一鋪清袋！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺克警方面：利用鄉黑同香港人打個兩敗俱傷，目的令香港人仇視佢地班牛屎人，引香港人反擊。用一招借刀殺人，想香港人對元朗黑勢力重挫，日後反黑易做嘢！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實無啦啦做咩會有班牛屎人今日先出黎做嘢，又啱見佢地之前出黎？<br />\n<br />\n另外想問 ，黑社會做嘢都喺睇錢姐，如果每人夾啲錢出黎，夾多個政府俾佢地，咁會唔會轉曬軚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b0579ede5b6bb80061c4ca65707458a6a88cf3","tid":1340852,"uid":70650,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30c97b642968e07a2a137d5ab60267195cef3bb","tid":1340852,"uid":267822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:16:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">響應罷工罷市罷課呀屌！！！<br />\n白衫人見市民出街胡亂打人！！！！<br />\n警賊唔lun理㗎啦！！！！！<br />\n文宣做野呀呀呀呀呀！！！！！</span>"},{"pid":"c99f4b0f34630beeba8e542de76e31116bc9ac16","tid":1340852,"uid":207374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80b0579ede5b6bb80061c4ca65707458a6a88cf3","tid":1340852,"uid":70650,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:19:23.000Z","msg":"爛仔交得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6474ec9fd48efca2558bf258e2a9ab3c6b9f7449","tid":1340852,"uid":207374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16